san josé state university conference services is designed to offer affordable and safe housing options for groups of all ages and size. no matter if you’re looking for overnight accommodations for your middle school students or an entire summer for your study abroad program, sjsu conference services is the perfect fit for you. we can even help set up meal plans and classrooms for your group's stay, while helping to meet your budgetary needs. please email uhs-conferenceassistant@sjsu.edu or call 408-795-5672 for any conference related questions. mon - fri 8:00am-5:00pm pst 